high_descs: Turn around and walk to the kitchen counter between the stove and refrigerator.
Pick up the gold colored wine glass by the toaster, on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the end of the kitchen, then turn right, facing the microwave.
Place the wine glass in the microwave.
Turn right and walk towards the stove, stopping at the end of the kitchen counter.
Pick up the wine glass on the kitchen counter, between the sink and the fry pan.
Turn to your left and walk back to the end of the kitchen where the microwave is.
Place the wine glass in the microwave with the other one.
anns.task_desc: Put two wine glasses in the microwave.

high_descs: Move to stand in front of the stove.
Pick up the wine glass from the counter to the right of the stove.
Carry the wine glass to the microwave, which is left of the sink.
Place the wine glass in the microwave.
Move to stand in front of the counter space between the sink and stove.
Pick up the wine glass from the counter.
Carry the wine glass back over to the microwave again.
Place the wine glass inside the microwave with the other one.
anns.task_desc: Move two wine glasses to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around towards sink, go to stove and counter on the right.
Pick up cup from the back of the counter behind the salt and pepper shakers.
Turn around, go along the counter, turn right to face the microwave.
Open microwave, put cup in to the left of the apple, close the microwave.
Turn around, head toward the stove, turn left towards the counter.
Pick up cup from counter.
Turn around, walk along the counter, turn right to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, put cup to the right and behind the apple in the microwave, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place two cups in the microwave.
